# 💊 MedVision - AI-Based Medicine Recognition Android App

MedVision is an Android app that uses machine learning to recognize medicines from images. It helps users identify tablets or capsules by capturing or uploading an image and retrieving relevant medical information.

---

## 🔍 Features

- 📷 Capture or upload medicine image
- 🧠 AI-based model to identify medicines (CNN / TFLite)
- 💡 Displays medicine name, usage, dosage info, and precautions
- 🌐 Optional: fetch drug data from online APIs
- 🗂 History of scanned medicines
- 📱 Built in Android Studio using Kotlin

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack

| Layer        | Tech Used                        |
|--------------|----------------------------------|
| ML Model     | TensorFlow Lite (TFLite)         |
| UI/UX        | Kotlin, XML Layouts              |
| ML Inference | ML Kit / TFLite Interpreter      |
| IDE          | Android Studio                   |
| Optional API | RxNorm API / OpenFDA (optional)  |

---

